projects.description:
For this project, I was responsible for finding a solution on how to best organize the knowledge management and training at the organization to remain adaptable. 

Some responsibilities included: 
- creating a survey that examines the effectiveness of the trainings in the company;
- designing an intervention that would encourage peer mentoring and facilitate tacit knowledge transfer;
- evaluating the advantages and disadvantages of each intervention and estimate the implementation costs;
- designing an interactive presentation template for EuroDev.

My responsibilities included but were not limited to: 

- rebranding job vacancies in terms or wording, content and layout;
- coming up a new recruitment strategy;
- creating a visually-appealing brochure; 
- finding candidates for the position through LinkedIn, analyzing CVs and profiles of the selected candidates; 
- designing and conducting interviews.
